========== EFS MOUNTED ON EC2 INSTANCE ===============

step -1
go to the EFS service 
and create EFS as per your requirements
go to the security group of efs allow port nfs 2049 


step -2 
launch ec2 instance save availability zone that you create efs
then take ssh
the 
#vi /etc/fstab
